Fourth Department,

September, 1943.

(September 22, 1943.) Sydney Cooper, as Trustee in Bankruptcy of Benjamin F. and Jessie Barnett, Respondent-Appellant, v. Georgia E. Cantrell et al., Appellants-Respondents, and Baldwinsville State Bank, Defendant-Respondent.
